<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 06:14:49 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>贸易部长表示，如果印度经济符合世贸组织规定，印度愿意加入中国贸易集团</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-open-joining-trade-blocs-with-china-if-its-economy-is-wto-compliant-trade-2024-03-28/</link><description>印度贸易部长皮尤什·戈亚尔 (Piyush Goyal) 在周四的一次媒体活动中表示，如果北京确保其经济开放、透明并遵守世界贸易组织的规则，印度愿意加入包括中国在内的贸易集团。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 06:09:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-open-joining-trade-blocs-with-china-if-its-economy-is-wto-compliant-trade-2024-03-28/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲交易枯竭之际，印度在全球股权资本市场上炙手可热</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/india-sizzles-global-equity-capital-markets-amid-deals-drought-asia-2024-03-28/</link><description>银行家表示，印度大量的大宗交易和上市（例如现代汽车旗下 30 亿美元的 IPO）将吸引更多资金进入印度市场，该市场今年在全球股权资本市场交易中所占的份额已创历史新高。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 05:43:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/india-sizzles-global-equity-capital-markets-amid-deals-drought-asia-2024-03-28/</guid></item><item><title>马来西亚对将中国主导的铁路项目延伸至泰国边境持开放态度</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/malaysia-open-extending-china-led-rail-project-thai-border-2024-03-28/</link><description>马来西亚政府表示，将考虑将中国主导的价值100亿美元的铁路项目延伸至其与泰国的边境，以促进东南亚邻国之间的经济联系。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 05:25:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/malaysia-open-extending-china-led-rail-project-thai-border-2024-03-28/</guid></item><item><title>独家：美国情报官员告诉参议员，中国药明康德与北京共享美国客户的数据</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-wuxi-apptec-shared-us-clients-data-with-beijing-us-intelligence-officials-2024-03-28/</link><description>据两位消息人士透露，美国情报官员二月底告诉正在制定一项生物技术安全法案的参议员，中国制药公司药明康德在未经北京同意的情况下将美国知识产权转让给北京。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 05:04:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-wuxi-apptec-shared-us-clients-data-with-beijing-us-intelligence-officials-2024-03-28/</guid></item><item><title>受中国和日本销量下滑影响，丰田 2 月份全球销量下滑 7%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/toyotas-global-sales-slide-7-february-led-by-slumps-china-japan-2024-03-28/</link><description>丰田汽车2月份全球销量同比下降7%，原因是农历新年假期导致中国销量大幅下滑，以及小型汽车部门安全测试丑闻导致日本销量下滑。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 04:32:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/toyotas-global-sales-slide-7-february-led-by-slumps-china-japan-2024-03-28/</guid></item><item><title>美国国防部长重申支持菲律宾，谴责中国行为“危险”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-defence-chief-reaffirms-support-philippines-chides-dangerous-chinese-conduct-2024-03-28/</link><description>美国国防部长劳埃德·奥斯汀重申了华盛顿对与菲律宾签署共同防御条约的承诺，并批评中国上周使用高压水枪并破坏菲律宾补给任务的行为是“危险的”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 03:49:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-defence-chief-reaffirms-support-philippines-chides-dangerous-chinese-conduct-2024-03-28/</guid></item><item><title>摩根大通任命 Rita Chan 和 Alan Ho 为中国联席高级国家官员</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/jpmorgan-appoints-rita-chan-alan-ho-china-co-senior-country-officers-2024-03-28/</link><description>根据路透社周四看到的一份备忘录，摩根大通已任命 Rita Chan 和 Alan Ho 为中国区联席高级官员。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 03:33:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/jpmorgan-appoints-rita-chan-alan-ho-china-co-senior-country-officers-2024-03-28/</guid></item><item><title>官员称中国将成为世界经济复苏的动力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-economy-will-provide-strong-driving-force-world-recovery-2024-03-28/</link><description>中国最高立法委员赵乐际周四表示，中国今年的目标是成为世界经济复苏的强劲动力，向外国投资者扩大开放市场，促进高质量增长。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 02:50:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-economy-will-provide-strong-driving-force-world-recovery-2024-03-28/</guid></item><item><title>台湾认为无论谁赢得选举，美国的支持都不会改变</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-sees-us-support-unchanged-no-matter-who-wins-election-2024-03-28/</link><description>台湾外交部周四表示，相信无论谁赢得总统选举，美国的支持都将保持不变，但随着竞选活动的升温，台湾将继续警惕台湾与中国问题被“操纵”的情况。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 02:45:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-sees-us-support-unchanged-no-matter-who-wins-election-2024-03-28/</guid></item><item><title>日元受到干预观察；亚洲股市低迷</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-03-28/</link><description>日元周四跌至近几十年来的最低水平，尽管日本当局的干预威胁让投资者对将日元推至新低持谨慎态度，而亚洲股市在美国关键通胀数据公布之前下跌。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 02:24:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-03-28/</guid></item><item><title>中国设定的人民币汇率远强于市场预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/china-sets-yuan-much-stronger-fixing-than-markets-expected-2024-03-28/</link><description>随着当局加大力度防止人民币大幅贬值，中国央行将人民币汇率设定为近五个月来的最大差距。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 02:13:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/china-sets-yuan-much-stronger-fixing-than-markets-expected-2024-03-28/</guid></item><item><title>中国希望荷兰确保光刻机贸易“正常”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-hopes-netherlands-will-ensure-normal-lithography-machine-trade-2024-03-28/</link><description>中国商务部部长王文涛表示，中方希望荷兰支持企业履行合同义务，确保光刻机贸易“正常”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 00:50:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-hopes-netherlands-will-ensure-normal-lithography-machine-trade-2024-03-28/</guid></item><item><title>小米在中国汽车的艰难时期进军电动汽车领域</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xiaomi-set-plunge-into-evs-tricky-time-china-autos-2024-03-27/</link><description>中国小米将于周四推出备受期待的电动汽车（EV），届时将公布定价并开始接受订单，这标志着这家电子公司进军汽车领域。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 23:02:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xiaomi-set-plunge-into-evs-tricky-time-china-autos-2024-03-27/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：日元大坝已决口，但并未决堤</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-03-27/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 21:47:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-03-27/</guid></item><item><title>美国新制裁针对朝鲜军事财政</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-north-korea-sanctions-target-individuals-russia-china-uae-based-firms-2024-03-27/</link><description>美国周三宣布对位于俄罗斯、中国和阿拉伯联合酋长国的六名个人和两个实体实施制裁，指责他们向朝鲜的武器计划提供资金。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 19:52:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-north-korea-sanctions-target-individuals-russia-china-uae-based-firms-2024-03-27/</guid></item></channel></rss>